  "answer": {
    "role": "assistant",
    "content": "<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<title>Hash Map Interactive Explorer</title>\n<style>\n/* Minimal, plain styling only to keep layout readable. No colors, no animations. */\nbody { margin: 8px; font-family: sans-serif; color: #000; background: #fff; }\nsection { margin-bottom: 12px; }\nlabel, button, select, input, textarea { font: inherit; }\nbutton { margin-right: 6px; }\ntable { border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 6px; }\ntd, th { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 4px 6px; }\n.small { font-size: 12px; }\n.controls-row { margin-bottom: 6px; }\ntextarea { width: 100%; height: 80px; }\ncode { font-family: monospace; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>Hash Map Interactive Explorer</h1>\n\n<section id=\"overview\">\n<p>This tool demonstrates a hash map with many interactive controls. You may choose hash functions, collision strategies (separate chaining, linear/quadratic probing, double hashing), insert/delete/search/update keys, step through probe sequences, rehash, undo/redo, import/export state, edit a custom hash function, and explore internal details like buckets and probe statistics. The interface is intentionally plain and functional.</p>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"config\">\n<h2>Configuration</h2>\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label for=\"modeSelect\">Collision Strategy:</label>\n<select id=\"modeSelect\">\n  <option value=\"separate\">Separate Chaining</option>\n  <option value=\"linear\">Open Addressing: Linear Probing</option>\n  <option value=\"quadratic\">Open Addressing: Quadratic Probing</option>\n  <option value=\"double\">Open Addressing: Double Hashing</option>\n</select>\n\n<label for=\"capacitySlider\">Capacity:</label>\n<input id=\"capacitySlider\" type=\"range\" min=\"3\" max=\"97\" value=\"11\">\n<span id=\"capacityValue\">11</span>\n\n<label for=\"loadThreshold\">Resize Threshold (load factor):</label>\n<input id=\"loadThreshold\" type=\"number\" min=\"0.1\" max=\"0.95\" step=\"0.05\" value=\"0.7\" style=\"width:70px\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label for=\"hashSelect\">Hash Function:</label>\n<select id=\"hashSelect\">\n  <option value=\"mod\">Modulo (numeric)</option>\n  <option value=\"sum\">String Sum</option>\n  <option value=\"poly\">Polynomial Rolling</option>\n  <option value=\"djb2\">DJB2</option>\n  <option value=\"custom\">Custom (JS)</option>\n</select>\n\n<label for=\"customHash\">Custom Hash (when selected):</label>\n<input id=\"customHash\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"function(key){ return ... }\" style=\"width:420px\">\n<button id=\"loadCustom\">Load Custom</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label for=\"keyType\">Key Type:</label>\n<select id=\"keyType\">\n  <option value=\"auto\">Auto</option>\n  <option value=\"string\">String</option>\n  <option value=\"number\">Number</option>\n</select>\n\n<label for=\"secondHash\">Second Hash (for double hashing):</label>\n<select id=\"secondHash\">\n  <option value=\"sum\">String Sum</option>\n  <option value=\"poly\">Polynomial Rolling</option>\n  <option value=\"djb2\">DJB2</option>\n  <option value=\"mod\">Modulo</option>\n</select>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"operations\">\n<h2>Operations</h2>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label for=\"keyInput\">Key:</label>\n<input id=\"keyInput\" type=\"text\" style=\"width:180px\">\n<label for=\"valueInput\">Value:</label>\n<input id=\"valueInput\" type=\"text\" style=\"width:180px\">\n<button id=\"insertBtn\">Insert</button>\n<button id=\"updateBtn\">Update</button>\n<button id=\"deleteBtn\">Delete</button>\n<button id=\"searchBtn\">Search</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<button id=\"bulkImportBtn\">Bulk Insert (lines: key,value)</button>\n<input id=\"bulkText\" type=\"text\" placeholder=\"e.g. a,1;b,2\" style=\"width:400px\">\n<button id=\"generateRandom\">Generate Random N</button>\n<input id=\"randomCount\" type=\"number\" min=\"1\" max=\"1000\" value=\"10\" style=\"width:70px\">\n<button id=\"clearBtn\">Clear Map</button>\n<button id=\"rehashBtn\">Force Rehash (to capacity slider)</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<button id=\"stepPrevBtn\">Step Prev</button>\n<button id=\"stepNextBtn\">Step Next</button>\n<button id=\"runAllBtn\">Run Operation</button>\n<label for=\"stepDelay\">Delay ms:</label>\n<input id=\"stepDelay\" type=\"number\" value=\"300\" style=\"width:70px\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<button id=\"undoBtn\">Undo</button>\n<button id=\"redoBtn\">Redo</button>\n<button id=\"snapshotBtn\">Save Snapshot</button>\n<button id=\"restoreBtn\">Restore Snapshot</button>\n<button id=\"exportBtn\">Export JSON</button>\n<input id=\"importArea\" placeholder=\"Paste JSON and click Import\" style=\"width:360px\">\n<button id=\"importBtn\">Import JSON</button>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"autoResize\" checked> Auto Resize</label>\n<label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"showProbes\"> Show Probe Sequence</label>\n<label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"showTombstones\"> Show Tombstones</label>\n<label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"logDetailed\" checked> Detailed Logs</label>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"sequencer\">\n<h2>Operation Sequencer & History</h2>\n<p>Build a sequence of operations (Insert/Delete/Search/Update) to run step-by-step. Each run produces probe-level steps that you can step through.</p>\n\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<select id=\"opType\">\n  <option value=\"insert\">Insert</option>\n  <option value=\"delete\">Delete</option>\n  <option value=\"search\">Search</option>\n  <option value=\"update\">Update</option>\n</select>\n<input id=\"opKey\" placeholder=\"key\" style=\"width:160px\">\n<input id=\"opValue\" placeholder=\"value (optional)\" style=\"width:160px\">\n<button id=\"addOpBtn\">Add to Sequence</button>\n<button id=\"clearSeqBtn\">Clear Sequence</button>\n<button id=\"runSeqBtn\">Run Sequence</button>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<label for=\"sequenceList\">Sequence:</label>\n<select id=\"sequenceList\" size=\"6\" style=\"width:100%\"></select>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"visual\">\n<h2>Map Visualization</h2>\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<label for=\"showBuckets\">Bucket Range (start,end):</label>\n<input id=\"showStart\" type=\"number\" value=\"0\" style=\"width:70px\">\n<input id=\"showEnd\" type=\"number\" value=\"10\" style=\"width:70px\">\n<button id=\"refreshView\">Refresh View</button>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"mapStats\" class=\"small\"></div>\n<div id=\"mapView\"></div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"details\">\n<h2>Details, Probes & Logs</h2>\n<div>\n<label>Probe Sequence (for last operation):</label>\n<pre id=\"probeView\" class=\"small\"></pre>\n</div>\n<div>\n<label>Operation Log:</label>\n<pre id=\"logView\" class=\"small\"></pre>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"custom\">\n<h2>Custom Hash Function Editor</h2>\n<p>When Hash Function = Custom, provide JavaScript function body or full function. It will be used as: userHash(key) and must return a non-negative integer.</p>\n<textarea id=\"customEditor\">function(key){\n  // Example: simple sum of char codes\n  var s = typeof key === 'string' ? key : String(key);\n  var h = 0;\n  for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++){ h = (h * 31 + s.charCodeAt(i)) & 0xffffffff; }\n  return Math.abs(h);\n}</textarea>\n<div class=\"controls-row\">\n<button id=\"applyEditor\">Apply Editor</button>\n<button id=\"testHashBtn\">Test Hash</button>\n<input id=\"testHashKey\" placeholder=\"test key\" style=\"width:200px\">\n<span id=\"testHashOutput\"></span>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<script>\n// Core Hash Map Implementation with interactive controls and step sequencing.\n\n// Utility functions\nfunction shallowCopy(v){ return JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(v)); }\nfunction isNumberLike(s){ return !isNaN(parseFloat(s)) && isFinite(s); }\nfunction clamp(v,a,b){ return Math.max(a,Math.min(b,v)); }\nfunction nextPrime(n){\n  function isPrime(x){\n    if(x<2) return false;\n    for(var i=2;i*i<=x;i++) if(x%i===0) return false;\n    return true;\n  }\n  var t = Math.max(2, Math.floor(n));\n  while(!isPrime(t)) t++;\n  return t;\n}\n\n// Hash functions\nvar HashFunctions = {\n  mod: function(key){\n    var k = (typeof key === 'number') ? key : parseFloat(key);\n    if(isNaN(k)) k = 0;\n    return Math.floor(Math.abs(k));\n  },\n  sum: function(key){\n    var s = String(key);\n    var h=0;\n    for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++) h += s.charCodeAt(i);\n    return Math.abs(h);\n  },\n  poly: function(key){\n    var s = String(key);\n    var h=0;\n    for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++) h = (h*31 + s.charCodeAt(i)) & 0xffffffff;\n    return Math.abs(h);\n  },\n  djb2: function(key){\n    var s = String(key);\n    var h = 5381;\n    for(var i=0;i<s.length;i++) h = ((h<<5)+h) + s.charCodeAt(i);\n    return Math.abs(h);\n  },\n  custom: null\n};\n\n// Data model and state\nvar State = {\n  mode: 'separate', // collision strategy\n  capacity: 11,\n  loadThreshold: 0.7,\n  hashName: 'mod',\n  secondHashName: 'sum',\n  keyType: 'auto',\n  autoResize: true,\n  showProbes: false,\n  showTombstones: false,\n  logDetailed: true\n};\n\n// HashMap class\nfunction HashMap(mode, capacity){\n  this.mode = mode || 'separate';\n  this.capacity = Math.max(3, capacity || 11);\n  this.size = 0;\n  this.buckets = new Array(this.capacity);\n  this.tombstones = 0; // for open addressing\n  this.clearBuckets();\n}\nHashMap.prototype.clearBuckets = function(){\n  if(this.mode === 'separate'){\n    for(var i=0;i<this.capacity;i++) this.buckets[i] = []; // arrays of {k,v}\n  } else {\n    for(var i=0;i<this.capacity;i++) this.buckets[i] = null; // null empty, {k,v,del:false} or {del:true}\n  }\n  this.size = 0;\n  this.tombstones = 0;\n};\nHashMap.prototype.copy = function(){\n  var copy = new HashMap(this.mode, this.capacity);\n  copy.size = this.size;\n  copy.tombstones = this.tombstones;\n  copy.buckets = shallowCopy(this.buckets);\n  return copy;\n};\n\n// hashing helpers\nfunction computeHash(key, capacity, primaryFn, secondFn){\n  var h1 = primaryFn(key) >>> 0;\n  var idx1 = h1 % capacity;\n  var h2 = null;\n  var idx2 = null;\n  if(secondFn) { h2 = (secondFn(key)>>>0) % capacity; idx2 = h2 === 0 ? 1 : h2; } // ensure non-zero\n  return {h1:h1, idx1:idx1, h2:h2, idx2:idx2};\n}\n\n// Operation step types:\n// Each operation generates steps: probe attempts with details.\nfunction Operation(type, key, value){\n  this.type = type;\n  this.key = key;\n  this.value = value;\n  this.steps = []; // each step: {index, action, stateSnapshot, info}\n  this.result = null;\n  this.completed = false;\n}\n\nvar App = {\n  map: new HashMap('separate', 11),\n  history: [], // snapshots for undo\n  future: [], // redo\n  sequence: [], // queued high-level operations\n  currentOperation: null,\n  currentStepIndex: -1,\n  runningTimer: null,\n  snapshots: {},\n  logs: [],\n  init: function(){\n    // wire up UI\n    document.getElementById('capacitySlider').addEventListener('input', function(e){\n      var v = parseInt(e.target.value,10);\n      document.getElementById('capacityValue').textContent = v;\n    });\n    document.getElementById('capacitySlider').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      var cap = parseInt(e.target.value,10);\n      cap = nextPrime(cap);\n      App.setCapacity(cap);\n      document.getElementById('capacityValue').textContent = cap;\n      document.getElementById('capacitySlider').value = cap;\n      App.log('Capacity set to '+cap);\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('modeSelect').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      App.setMode(e.target.value);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('loadThreshold').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      App.setLoadThreshold(parseFloat(e.target.value));\n    });\n    document.getElementById('hashSelect').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      var v = e.target.value;\n      App.setHashName(v);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('secondHash').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.secondHashName = e.target.value;\n      App.log('Second hash set to '+e.target.value);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('keyType').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.keyType = e.target.value;\n      App.log('Key type set to '+e.target.value);\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('insertBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      App.enqueueOrRun('insert', document.getElementById('keyInput').value, document.getElementById('valueInput').value);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('updateBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.enqueueOrRun('update', document.getElementById('keyInput').value, document.getElementById('valueInput').value); });\n    document.getElementById('deleteBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.enqueueOrRun('delete', document.getElementById('keyInput').value); });\n    document.getElementById('searchBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.enqueueOrRun('search', document.getElementById('keyInput').value); });\n\n    document.getElementById('bulkImportBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var raw = document.getElementById('bulkText').value;\n      App.bulkInsertRaw(raw);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('generateRandom').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var n = parseInt(document.getElementById('randomCount').value,10) || 10;\n      App.generateRandom(n);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('clearBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.snapshotPush(); App.map = new HashMap(State.mode, State.capacity); App.log('Map cleared'); App.refreshAll(); });\n    document.getElementById('rehashBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.snapshotPush(); App.forceRehash(parseInt(document.getElementById('capacitySlider').value,10)); });\n\n    document.getElementById('stepPrevBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.stepPrev(); });\n    document.getElementById('stepNextBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.stepNext(); });\n    document.getElementById('runAllBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.runCurrentOperation(); });\n    document.getElementById('stepDelay').addEventListener('change', function(){ /* no-op */ });\n\n    document.getElementById('undoBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.undo(); });\n    document.getElementById('redoBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.redo(); });\n    document.getElementById('snapshotBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.saveSnapshot(); });\n    document.getElementById('restoreBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.restoreSnapshot(); });\n\n    document.getElementById('exportBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var j = App.exportState();\n      prompt('Copy JSON below:', j);\n    });\n    document.getElementById('importBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var t = document.getElementById('importArea').value;\n      try{ App.importState(t); App.log('Imported state'); }catch(err){ App.log('Import failed: '+err); }\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('addOpBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var t = document.getElementById('opType').value;\n      var k = document.getElementById('opKey').value;\n      var v = document.getElementById('opValue').value;\n      App.addToSequence(new Operation(t,k,v));\n    });\n    document.getElementById('clearSeqBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.sequence = []; App.refreshSequence(); });\n    document.getElementById('runSeqBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.runSequence(); });\n    document.getElementById('sequenceList').addEventListener('change', function(){ /* selection available */ });\n\n    document.getElementById('refreshView').addEventListener('click', function(){ App.refreshView(); });\n\n    document.getElementById('loadCustom').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var val = document.getElementById('customHash').value;\n      try{\n        var fn = new Function('return ('+val+')')();\n        if(typeof fn !== 'function') throw 'Not a function';\n        HashFunctions.custom = fn;\n        App.setHashName('custom');\n        App.log('Custom hash loaded');\n      }catch(err){ App.log('Failed to load custom hash: '+err); }\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('applyEditor').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var txt = document.getElementById('customEditor').value;\n      try{\n        var fn = new Function('return ('+txt+')')();\n        if(typeof fn !== 'function') throw 'Not a function';\n        HashFunctions.custom = fn;\n        App.setHashName('custom');\n        App.log('Custom editor applied');\n      }catch(err){ App.log('Editor apply failed: '+err); }\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('testHashBtn').addEventListener('click', function(){\n      var k = document.getElementById('testHashKey').value;\n      try{\n        var out = App.computePrimaryHash(k);\n        document.getElementById('testHashOutput').textContent = '-> '+JSON.stringify(out);\n      }catch(err){ document.getElementById('testHashOutput').textContent = 'Error: '+err; }\n    });\n\n    document.getElementById('showProbes').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.showProbes = e.target.checked;\n      App.refreshAll();\n    });\n    document.getElementById('showTombstones').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.showTombstones = e.target.checked;\n      App.refreshAll();\n    });\n    document.getElementById('logDetailed').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.logDetailed = e.target.checked;\n    });\n    document.getElementById('autoResize').addEventListener('change', function(e){\n      State.autoResize = e.target.checked;\n    });\n\n    // initial\n    App.map = new HashMap(State.mode, State.capacity);\n    App.log('Initialized map with capacity '+State.capacity);\n    App.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  // state setters\n  setMode: function(m){\n    State.mode = m;\n    var old = App.map;\n    App.snapshotPush();\n    App.map = new HashMap(m, App.map.capacity);\n    // try to migrate existing entries if possible\n    if(old){\n      // simple migration: iterate entries and re-insert\n      var items = App.extractEntriesFromRaw(old);\n      for(var i=0;i<items.length;i++){\n        App.instantInsert(items[i].k, items[i].v, App.map);\n      }\n    }\n    App.log('Collision mode set to '+m);\n    App.refreshAll();\n  },\n  setCapacity: function(c){\n    State.capacity = c;\n    App.snapshotPush();\n    App.forceRehash(c);\n  },\n  setLoadThreshold: function(v){\n    State.loadThreshold = v;\n    App.log('Load threshold set to '+v);\n  },\n  setHashName: function(n){\n    State.hashName = n;\n    App.log('Primary hash set to '+n);\n  },\n\n  // compute hash using chosen functions\n  computePrimaryHash: function(key){\n    var fn = HashFunctions[State.hashName];\n    if(!fn) fn = HashFunctions.mod;\n    var v = fn(key);\n    if(typeof v !== 'number' || !isFinite(v)) v = 0;\n    return v >>> 0;\n  },\n  computeSecondaryHash: function(key){\n    var fn = HashFunctions[State.secondHashName];\n    if(!fn) fn = HashFunctions.sum;\n    var v = fn(key);\n    if(typeof v !== 'number' || !isFinite(v)) v = 1;\n    return (v >>> 0) || 1;\n  },\n\n  // Insert helpers (instant, used during rehash)\n  instantInsert: function(key, value, mapInstance){\n    var map = mapInstance || App.map;\n    if(map.mode === 'separate'){\n      var h = computeHash(key, map.capacity, function(k){ return App.computePrimaryHash(k); }).idx1;\n      var bucket = map.buckets[h];\n      for(var i=0;i<bucket.length;i++) if(bucket[i].k === key){ bucket[i].v = value; return; }\n      bucket.push({k:key, v:value});\n      map.size++;\n    } else {\n      // open addressing insert (no step recording)\n      var capacity = map.capacity;\n      var primary = function(k){ return App.computePrimaryHash(k); };\n      var secondary = function(k){ return App.computeSecondaryHash(k); };\n      var ch = computeHash(key, capacity, primary, map.mode === 'double' ? secondary : null);\n      var i = ch.idx1;\n      var step = 0;\n      var placed = false;\n      var firstTomb = -1;\n      while(step < capacity){\n        var cell = map.buckets[i];\n        if(cell === null){\n          if(firstTomb >= 0){\n            map.buckets[firstTomb] = {k:key, v:value, del:false};\n            map.tombstones--;\n          } else {\n            map.buckets[i] = {k:key, v:value, del:false};\n          }\n          map.size++;\n          placed = true;\n          break;\n        } else if(cell && cell.del){\n          if(firstTomb < 0) firstTomb = i;\n        } else if(cell.k === key){\n          map.buckets[i].v = value;\n          placed = true;\n          break;\n        }\n        step++;\n        if(map.mode === 'linear') i = (ch.idx1 + step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'quadratic') i = (ch.idx1 + step*step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'double') i = (ch.idx1 + step * ch.idx2) % capacity;\n      }\n      if(!placed && firstTomb >= 0){\n        map.buckets[firstTomb] = {k:key, v:value, del:false};\n        map.tombstones--;\n        map.size++;\n      } else if(!placed){\n        // table full\n      }\n    }\n  },\n\n  // high-level enqueue or immediate run\n  enqueueOrRun: function(type, keyRaw, value){\n    var key = this.normalizeKey(keyRaw);\n    var op = new Operation(type, key, value);\n    // if in sequencer mode? We'll run immediately by default but still produce steps to step through\n    this.prepareOperation(op);\n    this.currentOperation = op;\n    this.currentStepIndex = -1;\n    this.runCurrentOperation();\n  },\n\n  // normalize keys according to keyType\n  normalizeKey: function(raw){\n    if(State.keyType === 'number'){\n      var n = parseFloat(raw);\n      return isNaN(n)? raw : n;\n    }\n    if(State.keyType === 'auto'){\n      if(isNumberLike(raw)) return parseFloat(raw);\n      return raw;\n    }\n    return String(raw);\n  },\n\n  // create steps for an Operation without mutating map (so we can step)\n  prepareOperation: function(op){\n    op.steps = [];\n    op.completed = false;\n    op.result = null;\n    var map = this.map;\n    var capacity = map.capacity;\n    var primaryFn = function(k){ return App.computePrimaryHash(k); };\n    var secondaryFn = function(k){ return App.computeSecondaryHash(k); };\n    if(map.mode === 'separate'){\n      var h = computeHash(op.key, capacity, primaryFn).idx1;\n      var bucket = map.buckets[h];\n      // step: inspect bucket, search for key\n      op.steps.push({index:h, action:'inspectBucket', info:{bucket: shallowCopy(bucket)}});\n      var foundIndex = -1;\n      for(var i=0;i<bucket.length;i++){\n        op.steps.push({index:h, action:'compare', info:{position:i, key:bucket[i].k}});\n        if(bucket[i].k === op.key){ foundIndex = i; break; }\n      }\n      if(op.type === 'insert'){\n        if(foundIndex >= 0) op.steps.push({index:h, action:'updateInBucket', info:{position:foundIndex}});\n        else op.steps.push({index:h, action:'appendToBucket', info:{}} );\n      } else if(op.type === 'search'){\n        op.steps.push({index:h, action:'finishSearch', info:{found: foundIndex >=0, position: foundIndex}});\n      } else if(op.type === 'delete'){\n        op.steps.push({index:h, action:'deleteFromBucket', info:{found: foundIndex >=0, position: foundIndex}});\n      } else if(op.type === 'update'){\n        op.steps.push({index:h, action:'updateOrInsert', info:{found: foundIndex >=0, position: foundIndex}});\n      }\n    } else {\n      // open addressing: step through probes\n      var ch = computeHash(op.key, capacity, primaryFn, map.mode === 'double' ? secondaryFn : null);\n      var i = ch.idx1;\n      var step = 0;\n      var firstTomb = -1;\n      var encountered = [];\n      while(step < capacity){\n        var cell = map.buckets[i];\n        op.steps.push({index:i, action:'probe', info:{step:step, cell: shallowCopy(cell)}});\n        if(cell === null){\n          // empty - stop\n          op.steps.push({index:i, action:'emptySlot', info:{firstTomb:firstTomb}});\n          break;\n        } else if(cell && cell.del){\n          if(firstTomb < 0) firstTomb = i;\n          op.steps.push({index:i, action:'tombstone', info:{pos:i}});\n        } else if(cell.k === op.key){\n          op.steps.push({index:i, action:'found', info:{position:i}});\n          break;\n        }\n        step++;\n        if(map.mode === 'linear') i = (ch.idx1 + step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'quadratic') i = (ch.idx1 + step*step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'double') i = (ch.idx1 + step * ch.idx2) % capacity;\n      }\n      // finalize action\n      if(op.type === 'insert'){\n        op.steps.push({index:i, action:'finalizeInsert', info:{firstTomb:firstTomb}});\n      } else if(op.type === 'search'){\n        op.steps.push({index:i, action:'finalizeSearch', info:{firstTomb:firstTomb}});\n      } else if(op.type === 'delete'){\n        op.steps.push({index:i, action:'finalizeDelete', info:{firstTomb:firstTomb}});\n      } else if(op.type === 'update'){\n        op.steps.push({index:i, action:'finalizeUpdate', info:{firstTomb:firstTomb}});\n      }\n    }\n    this.log('Prepared operation '+op.type+' on key '+String(op.key)+' with '+op.steps.length+' steps');\n  },\n\n  // Execute full operation (non-stepwise)\n  executeOperationComplete: function(op){\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    var map = this.map;\n    if(map.mode === 'separate'){\n      var h = computeHash(op.key, map.capacity, function(k){return App.computePrimaryHash(k);}).idx1;\n      var bucket = map.buckets[h];\n      var found = -1;\n      for(var i=0;i<bucket.length;i++) if(bucket[i].k === op.key){ found=i; break; }\n      if(op.type === 'insert'){\n        if(found>=0){ bucket[found].v = op.value; this.log('Insert replaced existing key in bucket '+h); }\n        else { bucket.push({k:op.key, v:op.value}); map.size++; this.log('Inserted at bucket '+h); }\n      } else if(op.type === 'update'){\n        if(found>=0){ bucket[found].v = op.value; this.log('Updated key in bucket '+h); }\n        else { bucket.push({k:op.key, v:op.value}); map.size++; this.log('Key not found, inserted at bucket '+h); }\n      } else if(op.type === 'delete'){\n        if(found>=0){ bucket.splice(found,1); map.size--; this.log('Deleted key from bucket '+h); }\n        else { this.log('Delete: key not found in bucket '+h); }\n      } else if(op.type === 'search'){\n        if(found>=0) this.log('Search: found in bucket '+h+' value='+bucket[found].v);\n        else this.log('Search: key not found in bucket '+h);\n      }\n    } else {\n      var capacity = map.capacity;\n      var ch = computeHash(op.key, capacity, function(k){return App.computePrimaryHash(k);}, map.mode === 'double' ? function(k){return App.computeSecondaryHash(k);} : null);\n      var i = ch.idx1;\n      var step = 0;\n      var firstTomb = -1;\n      var placed = false;\n      while(step < capacity){\n        var cell = map.buckets[i];\n        if(cell === null){\n          if(op.type === 'insert' || op.type === 'update'){\n            var target = (firstTomb >= 0) ? firstTomb : i;\n            if(firstTomb >= 0) map.tombstones--;\n            map.buckets[target] = {k:op.key, v:op.value, del:false};\n            map.size++;\n            placed = true;\n            this.log('Inserted at index '+target);\n          } else if(op.type === 'search'){\n            this.log('Search: not found after probing to empty slot '+i);\n          } else if(op.type === 'delete'){\n            this.log('Delete: not found after probing to empty slot '+i);\n          }\n          break;\n        } else if(cell && cell.del){\n          if(firstTomb < 0) firstTomb = i;\n        } else if(cell.k === op.key){\n          if(op.type === 'insert'){\n            map.buckets[i].v = op.value;\n            this.log('Insert replaced at index '+i);\n          } else if(op.type === 'update'){\n            map.buckets[i].v = op.value;\n            this.log('Updated at index '+i);\n          } else if(op.type === 'search'){\n            this.log('Search: found at index '+i+' value='+map.buckets[i].v);\n          } else if(op.type === 'delete'){\n            map.buckets[i].del = true;\n            map.tombstones++;\n            map.size--;\n            this.log('Deleted (tombstone) at index '+i);\n          }\n          placed = true;\n          break;\n        }\n        step++;\n        if(map.mode === 'linear') i = (ch.idx1 + step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'quadratic') i = (ch.idx1 + step*step) % capacity;\n        else if(map.mode === 'double') i = (ch.idx1 + step * ch.idx2) % capacity;\n      }\n      if(!placed && (op.type === 'insert' || op.type === 'update') && firstTomb >= 0){\n        map.buckets[firstTomb] = {k:op.key, v:op.value, del:false};\n        map.tombstones--;\n        map.size++;\n        this.log('Inserted at tombstone index '+firstTomb);\n      }\n    }\n    // auto-resize if necessary\n    this.checkAutoResize();\n  },\n\n  // Step execution controls\n  runCurrentOperation: function(){\n    var op = this.currentOperation;\n    if(!op) { this.log('No current operation to run'); return; }\n    // if operation prepared, run steps automatically with configured delay\n    var delay = parseInt(document.getElementById('stepDelay').value,10) || 200;\n    this.runningTimer = setInterval(function(){ \n      if(App.currentStepIndex >= op.steps.length-1){ clearInterval(App.runningTimer); App.runningTimer = null; App.log('Operation complete'); return; }\n      App.stepNext();\n    }, delay);\n  },\n\n  stepNext: function(){\n    var op = this.currentOperation;\n    if(!op) { this.log('No operation loaded for stepping'); return; }\n    if(App.currentStepIndex >= op.steps.length-1){ this.log('Already at final step'); return; }\n    App.currentStepIndex++;\n    var step = op.steps[App.currentStepIndex];\n    App.applyStepToView(step, false);\n    // If finalizing step, mutate actual map and register snapshot\n    var finalActions = ['appendToBucket','updateInBucket','deleteFromBucket','updateOrInsert','finalizeInsert','finalizeSearch','finalizeDelete','finalizeUpdate','finishSearch'];\n    if(finalActions.indexOf(step.action) >= 0){\n      // apply operation up to current step index (so final step mutates)\n      App.executeOperationComplete(op);\n      op.completed = true;\n      App.currentStepIndex = op.steps.length-1; // go to end\n      App.refreshAll();\n    }\n    App.refreshProbeView();\n  },\n\n  stepPrev: function(){\n    var op = this.currentOperation;\n    if(!op) { this.log('No operation loaded'); return; }\n    if(App.currentStepIndex <= -1){ this.log('Already at initial state'); return; }\n    // We only support undo by restoring pre-operation snapshot if we moved past finalization.\n    // For simplicity, if we've mutated the map we restore previous snapshot.\n    // If the op wasn't finalized yet, just move back in UI representation.\n    var step = op.steps[App.currentStepIndex];\n    App.currentStepIndex--;\n    // If op.completed was true, restore snapshot prior to operation (undo) since step traversal is out of sync.\n    if(op.completed){\n      App.undo();\n      // mark op not completed so user can step again\n      op.completed = false;\n    }\n    App.refreshProbeView();\n    App.refreshView();\n  },\n\n  applyStepToView: function(step, preview){\n    // preview-only: just update probe pane and highlight index in map view.\n    // We don't mutate actual map here except at finalization.\n    var s = 'Step action: '+step.action+' at index '+step.index+' info: '+JSON.stringify(step.info);\n    if(State.logDetailed) this.log(s);\n    this.refreshProbeView();\n    this.refreshView();\n  },\n\n  // sequencer\n  addToSequence: function(op){\n    this.sequence.push(op);\n    this.refreshSequence();\n  },\n  refreshSequence: function(){\n    var sel = document.getElementById('sequenceList');\n    sel.innerHTML = '';\n    for(var i=0;i<this.sequence.length;i++){\n      var o = this.sequence[i];\n      var opt = document.createElement('option');\n      opt.value = i;\n      opt.text = (i+1)+'. '+o.type+' key='+String(o.key)+' value='+String(o.value);\n      sel.appendChild(opt);\n    }\n  },\n  runSequence: function(){\n    if(this.sequence.length === 0) { this.log('Empty sequence'); return; }\n    var seq = this.sequence.slice();\n    var i = 0;\n    var runNextSeq = function(){\n      if(i>=seq.length) { App.log('Sequence completed'); App.refreshAll(); return; }\n      var op = seq[i++];\n      App.prepareOperation(op);\n      App.currentOperation = op;\n      App.currentStepIndex = -1;\n      // run through and finalize immediately\n      App.executeOperationComplete(op);\n      setTimeout(runNextSeq, 20);\n    };\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    runNextSeq();\n  },\n\n  // bulk helpers\n  bulkInsertRaw: function(raw){\n    // format: key,value;key2,value2 or lines separated. Try multiple separators.\n    var parts = raw.split(/\\n|;|\\|/);\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    var count = 0;\n    for(var i=0;i<parts.length;i++){\n      var p = parts[i].trim();\n      if(!p) continue;\n      var kv = p.split(',');\n      var k = kv[0] !== undefined ? kv[0].trim() : '';\n      var v = kv[1] !== undefined ? kv[1].trim() : '';\n      App.instantInsert(this.normalizeKey(k), v);\n      count++;\n    }\n    this.log('Bulk inserted '+count+' items');\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n  generateRandom: function(n){\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    var chars = 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz';\n    for(var i=0;i<n;i++){\n      var k = '';\n      var len = 1 + Math.floor(Math.random()*6);\n      for(var j=0;j<len;j++) k += chars.charAt(Math.floor(Math.random()*chars.length));\n      var v = Math.floor(Math.random()*1000);\n      this.instantInsert(k, v);\n    }\n    this.log('Generated '+n+' random entries');\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  // rehash\n  forceRehash: function(newCapacity){\n    newCapacity = Math.max(3, newCapacity || this.map.capacity);\n    newCapacity = nextPrime(newCapacity);\n    var old = this.map;\n    var items = this.extractEntriesFromRaw(old);\n    this.map = new HashMap(old.mode, newCapacity);\n    for(var i=0;i<items.length;i++) this.instantInsert(items[i].k, items[i].v, this.map);\n    this.log('Forced rehash to capacity '+newCapacity+' (migrated '+items.length+' entries)');\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  extractEntriesFromRaw: function(mapInstance){\n    var result = [];\n    var map = mapInstance || this.map;\n    if(map.mode === 'separate'){\n      for(var i=0;i<map.capacity;i++){\n        var b = map.buckets[i];\n        for(var j=0;j<b.length;j++) result.push({k:b[j].k, v:b[j].v});\n      }\n    } else {\n      for(var i=0;i<map.capacity;i++){\n        var cell = map.buckets[i];\n        if(cell && !cell.del) result.push({k:cell.k, v:cell.v});\n      }\n    }\n    return result;\n  },\n\n  // auto-resize threshold\n  checkAutoResize: function(){\n    if(!State.autoResize) return;\n    var load = this.map.size / this.map.capacity;\n    if(load > State.loadThreshold){\n      var newCap = nextPrime(this.map.capacity * 2);\n      this.log('Auto-resize triggered: load '+load.toFixed(3)+' > '+State.loadThreshold+', resizing to '+newCap);\n      this.forceRehash(newCap);\n    } else if(this.map.capacity > 11 && this.map.size < this.map.capacity * 0.2){\n      var newCap = nextPrime(Math.max(11, Math.floor(this.map.capacity / 2)));\n      this.log('Auto-shrink check: resizing to '+newCap);\n      this.forceRehash(newCap);\n    }\n  },\n\n  // logging & snapshots\n  log: function(s){\n    var ts = (new Date()).toLocaleTimeString();\n    var line = ts + ' - ' + s;\n    this.logs.push(line);\n    if(this.logs.length > 200) this.logs.shift();\n    document.getElementById('logView').textContent = this.logs.join('\\n');\n  },\n  snapshotPush: function(){\n    var snapshot = {\n      map: this.map.copy(),\n      state: shallowCopy(State)\n    };\n    this.history.push(snapshot);\n    if(this.history.length > 50) this.history.shift();\n    this.future = [];\n    this.log('Snapshot pushed. History length: '+this.history.length);\n  },\n  undo: function(){\n    if(this.history.length === 0) { this.log('Nothing to undo'); return; }\n    var snap = this.history.pop();\n    this.future.push({map: this.map.copy(), state: shallowCopy(State)});\n    this.map = snap.map;\n    Object.assign(State, snap.state);\n    this.log('Undo applied. History now '+this.history.length);\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n  redo: function(){\n    if(this.future.length === 0) { this.log('Nothing to redo'); return; }\n    var snap = this.future.pop();\n    this.history.push({map: this.map.copy(), state: shallowCopy(State)});\n    this.map = snap.map;\n    Object.assign(State, snap.state);\n    this.log('Redo applied.');\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  // snapshots map\n  saveSnapshot: function(){\n    var name = 'snap_'+(new Date()).getTime();\n    this.snapshots[name] = {map: this.map.copy(), state: shallowCopy(State)};\n    this.log('Saved snapshot '+name);\n    prompt('Snapshot id:', name);\n  },\n  restoreSnapshot: function(){\n    var key = prompt('Enter snapshot id to restore (see saved ids):');\n    if(!key) return;\n    var s = this.snapshots[key];\n    if(!s){ this.log('Snapshot not found: '+key); return; }\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    this.map = s.map;\n    Object.assign(State, s.state);\n    this.log('Restored snapshot '+key);\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  // import/export\n  exportState: function(){\n    var s = {\n      map: this.map.copy(),\n      state: State,\n      logs: this.logs\n    };\n    return JSON.stringify(s);\n  },\n  importState: function(json){\n    var parsed = JSON.parse(json);\n    if(!parsed.map) throw 'Invalid JSON: missing map';\n    var m = parsed.map;\n    var newMap = new HashMap(m.mode || State.mode, m.capacity || 11);\n    newMap.size = m.size || 0;\n    newMap.tombstones = m.tombstones || 0;\n    newMap.buckets = m.buckets || newMap.buckets;\n    this.snapshotPush();\n    this.map = newMap;\n    if(parsed.state) Object.assign(State, parsed.state);\n    if(parsed.logs) this.logs = parsed.logs;\n    this.refreshAll();\n  },\n\n  // visualization\n  refreshAll: function(){\n    document.getElementById('modeSelect').value = State.mode;\n    document.getElementById('capacitySlider').value = this.map.capacity;\n    document.getElementById('capacityValue').textContent = this.map.capacity;\n    document.getElementById('loadThreshold').value = State.loadThreshold;\n    document.getElementById('hashSelect').value = State.hashName;\n    document.getElementById('secondHash').value = State.secondHashName;\n    document.getElementById('keyType').value = State.keyType;\n    document.getElementById('showProbes').checked = State.showProbes;\n    document.getElementById('showTombstones').checked = State.showTombstones;\n    document.getElementById('logView').textContent = this.logs.join('\\n');\n    this.refreshView();\n    this.refreshProbeView();\n    this.refreshSequence();\n    this.refreshStats();\n  },\n\n  refreshStats: function(){\n    var s = 'Capacity: '+this.map.capacity+'  Size: '+this.map.size+'  Tombstones: '+this.map.tombstones+'  Mode: '+this.map.mode;\n    s += '  Load: '+(this.map.size/this.map.capacity).toFixed(4);\n    document.getElementById('mapStats').textContent = s;\n  },\n\n  refreshView: function(){\n    var start = parseInt(document.getElementById('showStart').value,10) || 0;\n    var end = parseInt(document.getElementById('showEnd').value,10) || Math.min(this.map.capacity-1, start+10);\n    start = clamp(start, 0, this.map.capacity-1);\n    end = clamp(end, start, this.map.capacity-1);\n    var table = document.createElement('table');\n    var hrow = document.createElement('tr');\n    hrow.appendChild(td('Index'));\n    hrow.appendChild(td('Content'));\n    table.appendChild(hrow);\n    for(var i=start;i<=end;i++){\n      var tr = document.createElement('tr');\n      tr.appendChild(td(String(i)));\n      var cont = '';\n      if(this.map.mode === 'separate'){\n        var b = this.map.buckets[i];\n        cont = b.length === 0 ? '(empty)' : b.map(function(x){return String(x.k)+' : '+String(x.v)}).join(' -> ');\n      } else {\n        var c = this.map.buckets[i];\n        if(c === null) cont = '(empty)';\n        else if(c && c.del) cont = '(tombstone)';\n        else cont = String(c.k)+' : '+String(c.v);\n      }\n      tr.appendChild(td(cont));\n      table.appendChild(tr);\n    }\n    var container = document.getElementById('mapView');\n    container.innerHTML = '';\n    container.appendChild(table);\n    this.refreshStats();\n  },\n\n  refreshProbeView: function(){\n    var el = document.getElementById('probeView');\n    if(!this.currentOperation) { el.textContent = 'No current operation prepared'; return; }\n    var op = this.currentOperation;\n    var idx = this.currentStepIndex;\n    var out = [];\n    out.push('Operation: '+op.type+' key='+String(op.key)+' value='+String(op.value));\n    out.push('Steps total: '+op.steps.length+'   Current step: '+(idx>=0?idx:'not started'));\n    out.push('--- Steps ---');\n    for(var i=0;i<op.steps.length;i++){\n      var s = op.steps[i];\n      var mark = (i === idx) ? '>> ' : '   ';\n      out.push(mark + i + ': ['+s.index+'] '+s.action + ' ' + JSON.stringify(s.info));\n    }\n    el.textContent = out.join('\\n');\n  },\n\n  applyViewerHighlight: function(){ /* placeholder for future highlight */ },\n\n  // helpers\n};\nfunction td(txt){ var c = document.createElement('td'); c.textContent = txt; return c; }\n\nApp.init();\nApp.refreshAll();\n\n</script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
